    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Truck Mechanic: Dangerous Paths》</strong>是一款机械师与卡车司机模拟器，唯一的侧重点在于卡车的机械功能。每一趟任务都是一次旅途，是对你应变能力及技巧的真正考验。驾驶卡车穿越风景如画、险象环生的真实南美路线。完成独特的货物运输任务。你能克服一路上的挑战，让你的卡车在极端的条件下保持行驶吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为一名世界级的机械师</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在路途中进行细致而逼真的修理工作：从发动机调整到更换轮胎。你可以使用各种工具和零件来进行诊断与修理。进行战略性思考，让你的卡车保持最佳状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/5f073b19d114f6d7949f6e3dec9c70bf.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/5f073b19d114f6d7949f6e3dec9c70bf.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/5f073b19d114f6d7949f6e3dec9c70bf.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>享受逼真的南美景色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勇敢踏上南美危险而又迷人的道路：野外自然逼真的景色、各种各样的地貌、昼夜循环、不断变化的天气状况。所有这些都会为你带来叹为观止的体验。但是别忘了征服泥泞道路、崎岖小路，以及尘土飞扬的内陆地区会对你的卡车造成损害，所以务必密切关注，别让它彻底报废了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/eeeab31267711385b499cf0e031ba71f.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/eeeab31267711385b499cf0e031ba71f.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/eeeab31267711385b499cf0e031ba71f.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>完成货运任务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作不会从天而降：查看贸易站和加油站，寻找有利可图的工作机会。赢得当地人的信任才能获得更好的合同。每次完成任务都会获得资金回报，你可以将这笔钱投入到卡车中，对其进行升级或改变样式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/ca414fc8c2dbfde85a468d17ecd75c3b.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/ca414fc8c2dbfde85a468d17ecd75c3b.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/ca414fc8c2dbfde85a468d17ecd75c3b.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开拓自己的道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >条条大路通罗马，至于如何到达目的地则完全取决于你自己。在美丽的荒野上寻找自己的路。但要做好万全准备：勇敢踏上未知道路的卡车司机必须精通修理与导航。寻找安全的道路：探索区域会获得不菲的收益，而且事后也不必浪费宝贵的时间修理卡车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/3f306896484b90a14507fcbb3ca5a4b5.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/3f306896484b90a14507fcbb3ca5a4b5.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/3f306896484b90a14507fcbb3ca5a4b5.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义卡车</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡车也可以玩出很多花样——前往车库，定义你自己的风格。更换车身套件并装饰车内空间。升级卡车，让其在崎岖的道路上展现出更好的性能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/49336c1d5b4c90df6d5069972d2c25a9.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/49336c1d5b4c90df6d5069972d2c25a9.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/49336c1d5b4c90df6d5069972d2c25a9.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>推动剧情发展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验沉浸式的活动，让你的道路机修冒险更令人难忘。每一份工作都会给你带来独特的驾驶与修理挑战。你能克服它们吗？测试下自己的勇气吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/7d3272ab2f541e85ceb7ef0dad8928b3.poster.avif?t=1772049092\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/7d3272ab2f541e85ceb7ef0dad8928b3.webm?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995680/extras/7d3272ab2f541e85ceb7ef0dad8928b3.mp4?t=1772049092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>做好准备：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在路途中修理与维护卡车的各个部件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在修理过程中，有超过1000个零件可以拆卸和重新组装。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琳琅满目的工具，从扳手、大砍刀，到绞盘，应有尽有。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为发动机和其他机制提供了超高的细节层次。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在陆地上运输一系列货物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在加油站加油。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五个广阔且完全开放的地点，可供你步行或驾驶卡车探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘而迷人南美景色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十条难度不一的路线，带你穿越崎岖的地形、森林小路和硬核的越野地区。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的剧情，让你陷入意想不到的境地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地点可获得新零件、隐藏点及奖励目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舒适的车库：属于你自己的行动基地及任务出发点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制卡车，包括车内空间自定义。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >民用波段无线电通信：打电话寻求帮助或联系你的助理。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家角色改进。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家角色声望系统及可互动的NPC。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态天气与昼夜循环。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
